title: Aegean Airlines announces summer 2016 Kiev service changes
text:
Aegean Airlines announces summer 2016 Kiev service changes   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
In summer 2016, Aegean Airlines changes its operation in Kiev. All flights will be operated to/from Kiev Borispil (KBP), instead of Zhulyany (IEV). The airline in summer season operates up to four weekly flights from Athens, 3 from Larnaca. 
Athens – Kiev A3968 ATH0930 – 1200KBP 320 4 A3968 ATH1345 – 1615KBP 320 13 A3958 ATH2345 – 0215+1KBP 320 6 A3959 KBP0315 – 0545ATH 320 7 A3969 KBP1250 – 1520ATH 320 4 A3969 KBP1705 – 1935ATH 320 13 
Day 6/7 operates from 02JUL16 
Larnaca – Kiev A3758 LCA2330 – 0230+1KBP 320 246 A3759 KBP0320 – 0620LCA 320 357 Day 4/5 operates from 08JUL16
